<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sticky Notes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/general_styles.css">
    <style>
        .container-supremeth{
            min-width: 1200px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
        .note{
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #021;
        }
        .domnitori{
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, hsl(163, 54%, 57%) 0px, hsl(163, 54%, 57%) 20px, hsl(163, 54%, 47%) 20px, hsl(163, 54%, 47%) 40px);
            grid-column: 2/5;
            grid-row: 1/2;
        }
        .reteta{
            background-color: hsl(230, 27%, 67%);
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, hsl(230, 27%, 67%) 0px, hsl(230, 27%, 67%) 20px, hsl(230, 27%, 57%) 20px, hsl(230, 27%, 57%) 40px);
            grid-column: 9/12;
            grid-row: 1/2;
        }
        .adjectiv{
            /* background-color: hsl(50, 40%, 63%); */
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, hsl(50, 40%, 63%) 0px, hsl(50, 40%, 63%) 20px, hsl(50, 40%, 53%) 20px, hsl(50, 40%, 53%) 40px);
            grid-column: 5/8;
            grid-row: 2/3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-lightgreen-frame">Home</a>
        <form action="/logout" method="get">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lightgreen-frame btn-logout">Log out</button>
        </form>
    </nav>
    <div class="container-supremeth">
        <div class="note domnitori">
            <p>"Alexandru cel Bun, Stefan cel Mare, Radu cel Frumos -- de cercetat pentru
                compunere la istorie pana pe 23.03.2012"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="note reteta">
            <p>Reteta pentru sarnici</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Branza de vaca - o cana</li>
                <li>3 oua</li>
                <li>Sare la ochi</li>
                <li>Soda la ochi</li>
                <li>Faina cam doua cani</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="note adjectiv">
            <p>adjectivul - parte de vorbire flexibila care aratÄƒ o insusire a unui obiect sau a unei fiinte si determina numele acestora, acordandu-se cu ele in gen, numar si caz; adjectiv calificativ. -- pentru limba romana de ce</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>